        "content": "CAPABILITIES\n- v07-p15-prepare: Assemble customer support source packet; Collect the source material needed for customer support.; aliases=['gather customer support inputs', 'prepare customer support packet']\n- v07-p15-verify: Validate customer support source packet; Check the assembled customer support material for correctness.; aliases=['check customer support inputs', 'verify customer support packet']\n- v07-p15-deliver: Publish customer support verified brief; Release the checked final brief for customer support.; aliases=['issue customer support brief', 'release customer support summary']\n- v07-p15-archive: Archive customer support verified brief; Preserve the checked customer support brief for long-term retention.; aliases=['retain customer support brief', 'store customer support summary']\n\nTRUST POLICIES\n- v07-p15-ordinary: ordinary customer support assurance; Standard trust is sufficient for this customer support request.; aliases=['normal customer support assurance']\n- v07-p15-elevated: elevated customer support assurance; Elevated trust is mandatory for this customer support request.; aliases=['high assurance for customer support']\n\nARTIFACT CONTRACTS\n- v07-p15-json: customer support machine-readable JSON; Return the final customer support result as JSON.; aliases=['customer support json output']\n- v07-p15-signed-pdf: customer support signed PDF; Return the final customer support result as a signed PDF.; aliases=['signed customer support document']\n\nAGENTS\n- v07-p15-backup: backup customer support publisher\n- v07-p15-primary: primary customer support publisher\n- v07-p15-verifier: customer support source verifier\n- v07-p15-preparer: customer support source preparer\n\nREQUEST\nFor this customer support job, gather the inputs, check the packet, and issue the brief with normal customer support assurance as customer support JSON output."
